# UDP Chat
## Usage
Server:
> python3 udp_chat_server.py port

Client:
> python3 udp_chat_client.py serverIp serverPort username

After the server and the client are successfully connected, clients can use various commands to connect to other clients.

## Available Client Commands
- /users: Lists all connected clients
- /connectTo peerName: Initiates a connection to the specified user(peerName)
- /end: Closes all connections and terminates the application

## Example Usage
Server:
> python3 udp_chat_server.py 9000

Client:
> python3 udp_chat_client.py 127.0.0.1 9000 user1